cat << EOF
A desktop environment(XPde) and a window manager(XPwm) for Linux. It 
tries to recreate the Windows XP interface to-the-pixel point, nothing 
more. 

No clipboard compatibility between Gtk and Qt applications, no emulation 
of Windows applications, no unification on the widgets of X applications, 
just a desktop environment and a window manager.
EOF
